I had a dream with Missy in it. I don't remember it as well as I could have, for I woke up, then fell asleep again and had more dreams.

I was in an elevator going up, with two security guards alongside me. I had applied for a security job and this was going to be some sort of interview, I believe. I got out of the elevator to what I expected was going to be a room with an executive in it, but instead was a hallway leading to another elevator. I enter that elevator, and the two security guards in it are very reminiscent of the men in black from Deus Ex: very pale with unusual voices. One's a tall woman, and one's a short child.
I get very nervous and say something like "Haha, I don't think I'm suitable for this job, never mind!" and since the doors of the elevator are still open, I walk back out. But instead of the black-walled hallway, just because it's a dream, it's now a larger room, with many couches in it, and materials for a pillow fort. There's also a few normal people hanging around. The sort you'd expect to see around pillow forts.
I try to hide from my embarrassment, fear, and shame by hiding behind a couch where someone from the elevator would no longer be able to see me. Sitting, with knees close.
I see Missy, and her face has the cute proportions she often has in the traditional media art of her. Round cute face. Long limbs, as always. But she begins pouting at me. I forget why she was upset at me now, but I think it was because I hadn't given her something, in the past.
I begin to stack big pillows around and atop myself to totally hide from the world, but Missy begins raking her claws atop my head, drawing blood. (by accident?)

I've read multiple stories here, but haven't read HATSSSSSSS yet. Sorry about your characters not being there instead, writebros.
